  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.0.0-alpha02\" data-text=\"Version 1.0.0-alpha02\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.0.0-alpha02</h3>\n<p>March 13, 2019</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.viewpager2:viewpager2:1.0.0-alpha02</code> is released.  The full list of commits included in this version can be found <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/965e50ae02ab8c0821aa6db4d3296630ee8f4742..a6c93820c879141a92612abcf559a1993ceeb716/viewpager2\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>New features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ability to disable user input (<code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">setUserInputEnabled</code>, <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">isUserInputEnabled</code>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>API changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>ViewPager2 class final</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bug fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">FragmentStateAdapter</code> stability fixes</li>\n</ul>",
